title: Proxmox VE: Node LVM Filesystems
agents: proxmox_ve
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the filesystem usage of LVM-based storage on Proxmox VE nodes.
 It reports disk space usage, free space, and utilization percentages for each LVM
 filesystem configured as storage in Proxmox VE.
 LVM filesystems are storage backends of type "lvm" or "lvm-thin".

discovery:
 One service per LVM filesystem is created.
